message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and valued at $12000. Considering its exceptional quality and the benefits it provides, I believe we can come to an agreement that is mutually beneficial. I am proposing to sell it to you for $11000. This offer includes a comprehensive warranty and personalized support to ensure you get the most out of your investment. Please let me know if this proposal suits your budget and expectations.
